com.bobman159.rundml.core.expressions

Interface IMathExpression

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ICaseWhenValue, IExpressionNode, ISQLType
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MathExpression

    public interface IMathExpression
extends IExpressionNode
    A mathematical expression for operations such as add, subtract, multiply and divide in an SQL expression.
